.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include <SDL3_shadercross/SDL_shadercross.h>
.PP
.BI "void * SDL_ShaderCross_CompileDXBCFromHLSL(
.BI "    const SDL_ShaderCross_HLSL_Info *info,
.BI "    size_t *size);
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
You must SDL_free the returned buffer once you are done with it\[char46]
